                    Vision</div>
                <div class="fs-4 text-start mx-4 text-justify fw-bold" style="color: rgb(70, 7, 7); font-family: 'KoHo', sans-serif;"> <br> We see all the women
                    and youth getting fair opportunities to explore and pursue their dreams in technology. We believe
                    that women make up an enormous part of the demographics and influence the majority of needs of the
                    society. Their representation in tech is essential for companies to perform better organizationally.
                    Achieving gender diversity in tech is what we are ultimately aiming for. </div>
                <br>
            </div>
            
        </div>
