                <div class="fs-2 mt-3 fw-bolder px-3"
                    style="color: rgb(107, 20, 20); font-family: 'Zen Dots', cursive;">
                    Mission</div>
                <div class="fs-4 text-start mx-4 text-justify fw-bold" style="color: rgb(70, 7, 7);font-family: 'KoHo', sans-serif;"> <br>We are working to
                    expand access to opportunities in tech for young women. We aim at making use of all the available
                    resources to reach out to women and encourage them to get into technical fields.
                    We are stepping forward to building up confidence in women by helping them acquire the necessary
                    skills and introducing them to the perks of working in the technical industry and making them
                    realize how they can be a great asset, a positive change, to the society by being a part of it. We
                    still have a very long way to go, but it's achievable and so shall we.
                </div>
                <br>
            </div>

